Package: snpregR
Type: Package
Title: Stepwise Noise Peeling for Nadaraya-Watson Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given = "Bistoon",
      family = "Hosseini",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "bistoon.hosseini@gmail.com"
    )
Description: 
    Implements the Stepwise Noise Peeling (SNP) algorithm for 
    Nadaraya-Watson nonparametric regression. The package provides 
    bandwidth selection using the SNP procedure as well as the 
    direct Generalized Cross-Validation (DGCV) method. Utilities 
    for evaluating prediction accuracy and reproducing numerical 
    experiments from the accompanying paper are included.
